    "description": "<strong>Drone Warfare</strong> is an action focused flight sim and tower defense hybrid set in the near future.<br><br>Being the newest recruit to <strong>Project Helix</strong>, you are tasked with protecting the last honey bee colonies as they near extinction. Failure is not an option as depleting crops and widening food shortages are threatening humanity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/3d3f22c82978aad027249dd196141024.poster.avif?t=1744714891\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/3d3f22c82978aad027249dd196141024.webm?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/3d3f22c82978aad027249dd196141024.mp4?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are the remote pilot of the <strong>H-BEE 01 Drone Prototype</strong>, a tiny military flying machine that resembles a honey bee itself. Utilising nano-technology the drone packs an array of powerful weapons and advanced systems for the mission ahead.<br><br>The H-BEE drone is a last ditch attempt to protect what's left of the bee species. Can the dire situation be reversed somehow? And what exactly caused them to disappear in the first place?<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stunning environments for you to explore from an insect's eye view.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/ffbd3c46baa1dd6cca7c0afb252856dd.poster.avif?t=1744714891\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/ffbd3c46baa1dd6cca7c0afb252856dd.webm?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/ffbd3c46baa1dd6cca7c0afb252856dd.mp4?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>A diverse set of missions covering recon, defense, interception, and all out war!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/9d02cb96623bb33caec20827a8988f2b.poster.avif?t=1744714891\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/9d02cb96623bb33caec20827a8988f2b.webm?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/9d02cb96623bb33caec20827a8988f2b.mp4?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Deploy over-the-top weaponry and turrets to wreak havoc as you protect the bees from overwhelming odds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/4327f46522253fed048727e41526945d.poster.avif?t=1744714891\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/4327f46522253fed048727e41526945d.webm?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/4327f46522253fed048727e41526945d.mp4?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Complex flight mechanics that can be adjusted to suit your playing style.</li></ul><br><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong><br>Although action focused, Drone Warfare also includes the following gameplay features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tower defense elements. Observe enemy patterns and setup turrets around the environment to counter them.<br></li><li>Extensive research and upgrade options for the turrets, your drone, and the bee's themselves.<br></li><li>Full campaign story with vocal narrative.<br></li><li>Dynamic soundtrack.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/84b7c31c2b5ebaa13c5f488848bd6e6b.poster.avif?t=1744714891\" width=462 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/84b7c31c2b5ebaa13c5f488848bd6e6b.webm?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/84b7c31c2b5ebaa13c5f488848bd6e6b.mp4?t=1744714891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
